{"tid":954252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"的哥? 的你老母咩, 的士司機就的士司機啦","createTime":"2018-12-24T12:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T07:59:58.000Z","uid":120117,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da9ba59459bf521f4ddf299846a3ba6416277abf","tid":954252,"uid":120117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:55:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味, 岩岩上網睇新聞見到「的哥」, 心諗屌你老母咩, 的士司機就的士司機啦, <br />\n發覺依家D撚屌報紙佬真係慢慢用撚晒D支那用語, 正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎好快真係同支那接軌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3aS4M9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3aS4M9.jpg&h=80f105d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「的哥」是誰？「的姐」是誰？可能讀者們不大了解。在內地，男的士司機，叫「的哥」﹔女的士司機，叫「的姐」。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/~pth/pth_passage01.php?passage=45\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fed.cuhk.edu.hk%2F~pth%2Fpth_passage01.php%3Fpassage%3D45&d=jj2gdENwcyF8UVQX%2BVtGpDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b19e863b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/~pth/pth_passage01.php?passage=45</a>"},{"pid":"0643697a8fa8878d6aaec5e060f980523791e99f","tid":954252,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"哥士的"},{"pid":"81bdc2a6c3be3901f16f79383caef849a3235877","tid":954252,"uid":32579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:57:49.000Z","msg":"Dc9就dc9啦"},{"pid":"56c9fb4da2b01c50902a26c24d691cb76d57385f","tid":954252,"uid":47169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"乜撚野的哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係講開的士司機 / 的士佬咩"},{"pid":"1547be980450543b40a1ecebe9975a69e859ecee","tid":954252,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"666🤙🏻"},{"pid":"